CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...7. Mrs. Gwendolyn Turner and Miss Edna Jackson served delicious A&P Coffee to visiting homemakers...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Crowd standing in front of A & P Food Company booth, featuring Red Circle Coffee advertisements overhead, in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
